          </div>
          <div style="flex: 1; border-left: 2px solid var(--border-grey); padding-left: var(--space-6);">
            <h4>Testing & Validation</h4>
            <p class="text-grey mb-0">Comprehensive testing including security audits, performance testing, and compliance validation. User acceptance testing with your team.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 4 -->
        <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-6);">
          <div style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 120px; text-align: right;">
            <span style="background: var(--bitcoin-orange); color: white; padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-md); font-weight: 600; font-size: var(--font-size-sm);">Weeks 17-20</span>
          </div>
          <div style="flex: 1; border-left: 2px solid var(--border-grey); padding-left: var(--space-6);">
            <h4>Launch & Optimization</h4>
            <p class="text-grey mb-0">Production deployment, monitoring setup, staff training, and post-launch optimization. Ongoing support and iterative improvements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-grey mt-8">*Timelines vary based on regulatory requirements and customization scope</p>
